Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.27,0:00:04.96,Location,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(367,0)\pos(362,359)}Deutsche Zukunft Newspaper Publishing\NCompany - Czech Branch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(357,460)}This case is becoming complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, anything new?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police say they'll hold a press conference at 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading to the Prague police station right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a case! I've never had such a case before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been looking for something in here all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I found the article I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... please wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Mr. X in this article...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. X?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This article from three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was trying to expose the truth behind the\Nformer Czechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Wall came down... the German right\Nwing's influence suddenly increased, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the former Czechoslovakian secret\Npolice established a crime syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote that article.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be possible to meet this member\Nof the former secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. X, who was interviewed in this article?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you're a special correspondent from Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to learn by meeting Mr. X?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of investigating... the circumstances\Nsurrounding the abductions and confinements...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that happened in this country during the Cold War.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're scary people, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I risked my life to interview them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, they're still scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, it created quite an uproar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know about Detective Suk's case?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some reporter you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you can't speak Czech...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're investigating the\Nremnants of the secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should have already heard the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. We published it in our paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can read German, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk, a young detective from the Prague police...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shot and killed two detectives of a special investigative\Nteam dispatched from police headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murder of Inspector Zeman turned out to be the clue\Nneeded to prove the dark connection between...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the former secret police and the current Czech police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, Suk was the one who revealed the relationship\Nbetween the former secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Prague police chief\Nand the other two policemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of them were conveniently poisoned,\Nand Suk distinguished himself in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the special investigative team was marking Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Suk killed the two policemen\Nwho were marking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The promising elite detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he distinguished himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you muttering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed three of his superiors with poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whisky bonbons...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A muscle relaxant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:37.76,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,200)\pos(363,352)}Tangent Point
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Jan Suk's mother here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you with the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in room 409.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Jan Suk's mother, aren't you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan, you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come closer and let me see your face, Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your son call or write you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. My neighbor, Katherina, hasn't\Ngiven me back my stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria gave me that precious stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you playing there again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always play detective there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may think it's your secret place, but I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deserted building on Brno Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be back in time for dinner, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a monster without a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster wanted a name so\Nbadly that he couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once upon a time, there was a monster without a name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you some food and a newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You became a star overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think anybody noticed\Nthat I sent my mom the tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the research data from the safety deposit box?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be safer with her than with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the events of your case are\Nvery similar to the other case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, in D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf, Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a hospital's director and two other doctors\Nall died from poisoned candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspect was a promising young surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still on the run, trying to prove his innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're better off than that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you have me for a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the stairs up to my flat, you saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful blonde girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that girl's the real murderer, we have to find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I'll be running for the rest of my lifel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this have to happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I supposed to disappear like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to have faith in yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you're the only one you can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I was little I used to pretend that I was a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the inspector's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised it's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd sit here and give orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like on the TV drama I watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's going to be a tough case this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want everyone to give it everything they've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not let evil prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure takes me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous by the window, so\Nlet's get you behind the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a goner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who fired that shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Czechoslovakian secret police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they shooting from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be fine, Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't hit anything vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to borrow your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're missing his vital organs on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tape isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can see us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here, Suk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming to help you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You should...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should save yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's about time we finish them off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, let 's wait a little longer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Czech...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Circle around to the right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We need another guy over here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tape!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's just bust in now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting hungry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't eaten lunch yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me neither!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's just break through the floor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's see, what should we eat?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, pass me the tools.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found a good Italian restaurant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyone got a smoke?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not in the mood for Italian.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, this drill's not working!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This cigarette sucks... I can't smoke this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What, Chinese food again?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get me a bigger tool, something like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:14:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not Chinese, it's Vietnamese!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you speak German?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer the question! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already entered the building...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to kill that young cop and the skinny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magnificent Steiner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magnificent Steiner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has done it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor, you finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you, please save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of other patients, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,living inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came from Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magnificent Steiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey kids, are you sitting in front of the TV?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what adventure awaits us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're in trouble, just call my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when or where, I'll he there to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Invincible Steiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive the evildoers, for my name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magnificent Steiner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always glued to the TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whenever "The Magnificent Sterner" came on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main character was a cowardly young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was always cornered by bad guys at crucial moments...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when he woke up, the bad guys had already\Nbeen beaten by the Magnificent Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without realizing it, he had become\Nthe Magnificent Steiner...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever he was in trouble, Steiner would appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and beat up all the bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I remember from my childhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that cartoon on TV, "The Magnificent Steiner."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All my other memories were completely erased...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by Kinderheim 511.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably couldn't care less, since\Nit doesn't concern you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I've given him all the emergency care I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the bullets passed through his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the arteries from under his armpit\Nto his upper arm are critically wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I've stopped the bleeding for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him to a hospital quickly so he can he treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you said that this doesn't concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinderheim 511 does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need another gurney over here! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the status of the wounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They need to be looked at soon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've all been given emergency care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was very precisely done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precise emergency care...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all in Czech.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only understood which hospital they took the patients to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jakub Zima Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the cops will probably arrest Suk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's innocent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go and testify...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma, why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, about what you said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind telling me about Kinderheim 511?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I don't really remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for little fragments here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dark hallway...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cracks in the ceiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of a door creaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A musty bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories only became clear some\Ntime after I had left the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone said it was when I was fourteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think back on it, I was put in a weird school...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where they gave me another name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolfgang Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My house was in an artificial neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were not allowed to leave the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone pretended to be my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone pretended to be my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was made to study many different languages...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Russian, English, Spanish, French...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spy training?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the things I was made to learn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what do you think was the toughest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we need to get to Suk's hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer, I saw it on the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wanted as a prime suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can prove Suk's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:31.22,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:44.65,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:44.65,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:47.61,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:23:01.29,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:23:01.29,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.89,0:23:26.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:34.57,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:37.03,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
